Interface Repository<T,ID>

Type Parameters:
T - generic type of Repository objects (entities).
ID - generic type of object identifier (id).
public interface Repository<T,ID>
Interface to access a collection of objects of a datamodel class of type T in a DataStore.

The interface provides CRUD operations (CRUD: Create, Read, Update, Delete).

The Repository interface is derived from Spring Boot's CRUDRepository interface.

Authors of original Spring Code :
Author:
Oliver Gierke, Eberhard Wolff, Jens Schauder
